[ProMED really fell for that one! What a difference one letter can make.
Crows are carrion feeders, but it is probably going too far to postulate
that they may be getting preferentially infected by eating dead rabbits or
rodents that are the actual reservoir of this strain. They may just be more
susceptible than other avian species - Mod.JW
